name: artifactory
description: As the first, and only, universal Artifact Repository Manager on the market, JFrog Artifactory fully supports software packages created by any language or technology. Documentation is available at: https://github.com/dcos/examples/
preInstallNotes: You will need at least 1 public agent in your cluster to install Artifactory-lb.
postInstallNotes: Artifactory has been installed. Please install Artifactory-lb if not already installed.
